                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "6849416011c8c26de22cca22c8c970e8",
                "text": "A creature with this trait is a member of the leshy ancestry. These small plant or fungus creatures are humanoid in form. An ability with this trait can be used or selected only by leshies. A weapon with this trait is created and used by leshies."
            },
